baby ignore karo ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
baby ignore karo  Example 06 — One-liner Conditionals
baby ignore karo  sun na agar ... toh ... warna ...
baby ignore karo  For quick checks without multi-line blocks.
baby ignore karo ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

yaad x hai 42
yaad name hai "Laila"
yaad online hai sach

~~ Basic one-liner
sun na agar x bada hai 0 toh bolo "positive" warna bolo "zero ya negative"

~~ With string comparison
sun na agar name barabar hai "Laila" toh baby bolo naa "Laila aagayi 💌" warna bolo "koi aur hai"

~~ With boolean
sun na agar online toh bolo "online ✅" warna bolo "offline 📴"

~~ Chained — note: one-liner is always a single if/else
yaad val hai 7
sun na agar val barabar hai 7 toh bolo "lucky number! 🍀" warna bolo "try again"

~~ Use it inside output
yaad a hai 10
yaad b hai 20
bolo "the bigger one is:"
sun na agar a bada hai b toh bolo a warna bolo b

love you baby byeee
